===Governors Award===
The Governors Award was presented to screenwriter, producer and director of film and television [[Greg Berlanti]] in recognition of his significant impact on television and culture by depicting the underrepresented in film.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.emmys.com/news/awards-news/76th-governors-announced-240822 |title=Greg Berlanti to Receive the 2024 Governors Award |publisher=[[Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]] |date=August 22, 2024 |access-date=August 22, 2024 |archive-date=September 29, 2024 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240929075933/https://www.emmys.com/news/awards-news/76th-governors-announced-240822 |url-status=live}}</ref>

